{"article_id":"acvf7GM400ENCnBR","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"FIRST ON CNN :","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Charges filed against Libyan militia leader Ahmed Abu Khattala , others","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"Attack","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"last September killed Ambassador Christopher Stevens and three other Americans","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"Authorities would not detail counts","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"as charges remain under seal","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"The Benghazi attack has become a political flashpoint in Washington","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Federal authorities have filed the first criminal charges in the investigation of the deadly terror attack on the U.S. diplomatic compound in Benghazi , Libya ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"people briefed on the matter","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"said .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"Several suspects","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"charged in the armed assault last September 11","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"include prominent Libyan militia figure Ahmed Abu Khattala ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"the sources said .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"Other identities were not disclosed .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"The counts","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"initially sought months ago in New York","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"are still under seal ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"according to the sources .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The investigation of the attack","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"that killed Ambassador Christopher Stevens and three other Americans","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"continues ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"these people said ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"as investigators try to build their case against Khattala and others","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"who","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"authorities believe","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"were involved .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Justice Department spokesman Brian Fallon declined to comment","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"as did FBI spokesman J. Peter Donald in New York .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"JUST WATCHED First charges in Benghazi attack","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"MUST WATCH First charges in Benghazi attack 04:55","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"JUST WATCHED Benghazi almost 1 year later","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"MUST WATCH Benghazi almost 1 year later 04:33","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"JUST WATCHED What is the truth about Benghazi ?","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"MUST WATCH What is the truth about Benghazi ?","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"01:43","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"But word of the development comes","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"as the Justice Department has come in for sharp criticism from congressional lawmakers about the pace and progress of the investigation .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Attorney General Eric Holder had earlier this year promised them","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"that the Justice Department would soon make public what actions","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"it would take .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Republicans have demanded more aggressive steps from the incoming FBI Director James Comey .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"But people close to the case said","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"the investigation has moved significantly in recent months .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"In that time , the FBI has released photos of what it called persons of interest","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"who were present during the attacks ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"seeking tips from the Libyan public .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"It could n't be learned when the United States plans to announce the charges","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"or whether there is any intention","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"to try to detain Khattala or the others .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"None of those briefed on the matter","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"would discuss the precise counts .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"In a recent interview with CNN 's Arwa Damon , Khattala acknowledged being at the Benghazi mission after the attack","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"but denied any involvement .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"Benghazi has become a political flashpoint in a long-running battle between the Obama administration and Republicans ,","depth":4},{"id":59,"text":"who accuse it of not bolstering security before the attack ,","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"of botching the response to it","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"and of misleading the public for political gain less than two months before the November election .","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"The investigation is led by agents from the FBI in New York","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"and has included some members of the Washington field office ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"who have traveled to Libya","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"to interview hundreds of witnesses ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"those briefed on the investigation","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"said .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Khattala told CNN","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that he had not been questioned by either Libyan authorities or the FBI .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"U.S. law enforcement officials said","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"it 's not unusual for the FBI not to seek to interview defendants in a case","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"while they collect other evidence .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"The Benghazi attack involved scores of militants","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"using rocket-propelled grenades and other weapons .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Stevens took refuge behind a fortified door with heavy metal bars","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"to keep the attackers from breaking in .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"But they set fire to the mission","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"-- a villa --","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"with diesel fuel .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Stevens was overcome by smoke .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"U.S. Rep. Adam Schiff , a Democratic member of the House Intelligence Committee , said in an interview on `` The Lead with Jake Tapper ''","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"that he would not describe the investigation as proceeding rapidly .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"`` It 's been frustrating for many of us","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"that it has n't moved faster ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"but it is a very difficult working environment for our agents , ''","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"said Schiff .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"`` Gathering evidence in Libya ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"you might imagine ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"is very difficult ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"finding , interviewing witnesses , extremely difficult . '' `` We have identified many of the parties involved .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"We 're still trying to identify what the command-and-control structure would be .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"A lot of missing pieces still ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"but we are finally making progress , ''","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"said Schiff .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":189,"left":0,"right":188,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":188,"left":151,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":123,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":101,"right":122,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":7,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":1,"right":99,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":97,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":2,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":120,"right":121,"relation":"elabor